high_descs: Turn around completely and walk forward. Turn to the left and then turn right at the counter to the sink.
Pick up the knife from the sink.
Turn to the left and walk forward.  Turn right and walk to the table.
Place the knife on plate on the table.
Pick up the plate and knife from the table.
Turn to the right and walk to the counter. Turn right and go to the sink.
Place the knife and plate in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place the knife and plate in the sink.

high_descs: Turn around, go straight, then left, then right to face the sink.
Pick up the yellow knife from the sink.
Go to the right, then turn around and go straight to face the white table.
Place the yellow knife on top of the white plate on the table.
Pick the white plate up from off of the white table.
Turn to the right, go straight then to the left to face the sink.
Place the plate with the knife on it in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place the white plate with the knife on it in the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and then turn left and face the sink on the right side.
Pick up the knife from inside the sink.
Carry the knife and turn to the right, then the right again to locate the white table.
Place the knife on the plate, that is close to the center.
Pick up the plate from the table.
Carry the plate and turn to the right and then the right again. Turn left and face the sink on the right side.
Place the knife and plate in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Move a knife and plate to the sink.
